targets.query: SELECT difference(qr)/10 as "QPS" FROM (SELECT sum(queryReq) AS "qr" FROM $database.."httpd" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(10s))

SELECT difference("count")/10 as "DML", difference("qr")/10 as "Query" FROM (SELECT sum(exec_run_time_count) as "count", sum(queryReq) AS "qr" FROM $database.."httpd", $database.."executor" WHERE app='ts-sql' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(10s) FILL(null))

SELECT difference("duration")/difference("qr")/1000000 as "latency" FROM (SELECT sum(queryReqDurationNs) AS "duration", sum(queryReq) AS "qr" FROM $database.."httpd" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(2m))

SELECT difference("runtime")/difference("count")/1000000 AS "DML", difference("duration")/difference("qr")/1000000 AS "Query" FROM (SELECT sum(exec_run_time_sum) AS "runtime", sum(exec_run_time_count) AS "count", sum(queryReqDurationNs) AS "duration", sum(queryReq) AS "qr" FROM $database.."httpd", $database.."executor" WHERE app='ts-sql' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(10s) FILL(null))

SELECT difference("AbortCount") AS "Abort", difference("FailedCount") AS "Failed", difference("TimeoutCount") AS "Timeout" FROM (SELECT sum(exec_abort_count) as "AbortCount", sum(exec_failed_count) as "FailedCount", sum(exec_timeout_count) as "TimeoutCount" FROM $database.."executor" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(10s))

SELECT difference("duration")/difference("count")/1000000 as "latency" FROM (SELECT sum(exec_run_time_sum) AS "duration", sum(exec_run_time_count) AS "count" FROM $database.."executor" WHERE app='ts-store' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(10s))

SELECT "hostname" as "host", top("last_count", 60) as "distribution" FROM (SELECT last(count) as "last_count" FROM (SELECT last(queryReq)-first(queryReq) AS "count" FROM $database.."httpd" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY "hostname") GROUP BY "hostname")

SELECT "hostname" as "host", top("last_count",60) as "distribution" FROM (SELECT last("count") as last_count FROM (SELECT max(exec_run_time_count)-min(exec_run_time_count) as count FROM $database.."executor" WHERE app='ts-sql' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "hostname") GROUP BY "hostname")

SELECT "hostname" as "host", top("last_count",60) as "distribution" FROM (SELECT last("count") as last_count FROM (SELECT max(exec_run_time_count)-min(exec_run_time_count) as count FROM $database.."executor" WHERE app='ts-store' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "hostname") GROUP BY "hostname")

SELECT difference(rows)/difference(count) FROM (SELECT sum(source_rows_sum) as rows, sum(exec_run_time_count) as count FROM $database.."executor" WHERE app='ts-sql' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(10s))

SELECT difference(rows)/difference(count) FROM (SELECT sum(source_rows_sum) as rows, sum(exec_run_time_count) as count FROM $database.."executor" WHERE app='ts-store' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(10s))
SELECT difference(rows)/difference(count) FROM (SELECT sum(sink_rows_sum) as rows, sum(exec_run_time_count) as count FROM $database.."executor" WHERE app='ts-sql' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(10s))

SELECT difference(rows)/difference(count) FROM (SELECT sum(sink_rows_sum) as rows, sum(exec_run_time_count) as count FROM $database.."executor" WHERE app='ts-store' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(10s))
SELECT sum("queryReqActive") AS "queryReqActive" FROM $database.."httpd" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) FILL(null)
SELECT sum("queryReqActive") AS "queryReqActive" FROM $database.."httpd" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval),"hostname" FILL(null)
SELECT mean("CpuUsage") AS "CPU" FROM $database.."system" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) FILL(null)
SELECT mean("MemUsage") as "Mem" FROM $database.."system" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m) FILL(null)
SELECT mean("CpuUsage")/64 FROM $database.."runtime" WHERE $timeFilter  and app = 'ts-store' GROUP BY time($__interval),"hostname" fill(null)
SELECT mean("CpuUsage") AS "CPU" FROM $database.."system" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), "host" FILL(null)
SELECT max("MemUsage") as "Mem" FROM $database.."system" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m), "host" FILL(null)
SELECT mean("NumGC") AS "NumGC" FROM $database.."runtime" WHERE $timeFilter  AND "hostname" =~ /8086/ GROUP BY time($__interval),"hostname" FILL(null)
SELECT mean("NumGC") AS "NumGC" FROM $database.."runtime" WHERE $timeFilter  AND "hostname" =~ /8401/ GROUP BY time($__interval),"hostname" FILL(null)
SELECT mean("NumGoroutine") AS "NumGoroutine" FROM $database.."runtime" WHERE $timeFilter AND "hostname" =~ /8086/ GROUP BY time($__interval), "hostname" FILL(null)
SELECT mean("NumGoroutine") AS "NumGoroutine" FROM $database.."runtime" WHERE $timeFilter AND "hostname" =~ /8401/ GROUP BY time($__interval), "hostname" FILL(null)
SELECT mean("connTotal") AS "mean_connTotal" FROM $database.."spdy" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), "hostname" FILL(null)

SELECT difference("duration")/difference("qr")/1000000 as "latency" FROM (SELECT queryReqDurationNs AS "duration",queryReq AS "qr" FROM $database.."httpd" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY  hostname) group by hostname
